    "body" : "<p>Use <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/lang/Deprecated.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>@Deprecated</code></a> on method.<br />\nDon't forget to add the <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/guide/javadoc/deprecation/deprecation.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>@deprecated</code></a> Javadoc tag:</p>\n<pre><code>/**\n * Does some thing in old style.\n *\n * @deprecated use {@link #new()} instead.  \n */\n@Deprecated\npublic void old() {\n// ...\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
